# Here I was prepared placeholder for CMS app. I will add more details later.

## My approach:

I will prepare cms based on markdown, and using shared components from `packages/ui`.

## Flow:

1. Create Article draft -> save in DB
2. Publish Article -> change flag in DB from `draft` to `published`
3. Tanstack Start create server-side entry and next hydrate aricles on client
4. Backend save uplouded data on redis to faster http comunication,
5. Markdown components displaying Article on client-side

You need all components for blog in `packages/`
